  - lockscreen/autolock
  - system log
  - file specifying init state of internal expansion pins

Docs:
  - specify the native API
  - specify all the used file formats:
    - basic "ini" style file
    - basic "csv" style file
    - Application:
      - list and describe used callbacks
    - Config files:
      - svp.cfg
